  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13069203/lapland-fact-file-march.jpg" alt="JanuaryHero" data-udi="umb://media/d8b4594313044df4adecb1b556f676b0" /></p>
<h2>Lapland in January</h2>
<p>Why go on holiday to Lapland in January? </p>
<ul>
<li>It's always nice to beat the January blues and have a holiday to look forward to.</li>
<li>In January, the slopes tend to be more quiet and free so you can <a data-udi="umb://document/5c4dcb32caa44c5096ed1fc9494f0b29" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c4dcb32caa44c5096ed1fc9494f0b29}" title="Skiing &amp; Snowboarding in Lapland, Finland">ski</a> until your heart is content without interruptions.</li>
<li>As January tends to be a quieter time, you will have lots of <a data-udi="umb://document/b977658fa8a04f9c9903cffdc2c187c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b977658fa8a04f9c9903cffdc2c187c2}" title="Lapland accommodation options">accommodation choices</a>, so you can pick your favourite!</li>
<li>Yes, January tends to be the coldest time of year, but therefore tends to be  the crispest, clear skies. Offering therefore stunning views of the scenery and surroundings.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Lapland deals</a></p>
<p>Enjoy a range of fun excursions - Lapland offers everything from Husky sleigh rides, meeting reindeer, a days skiing to an overnight trip in a glass igloo. View all the available excursions: </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" class="c-btn">Lapland excursions</a></p>
<h3>Best resorts in Lapland during January</h3>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Yllas</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108735/yllasjanuary-900x500.jpg" alt="YllasJanuary" data-udi="umb://media/94243497bd6746bc808fddbf67f34fcd" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Split into 3 areas: Äkäslompolo is to the north of the fell, Ylläsjärvi and Ylläsrinnie to the south side of the fell.</li>
<li>Hosting Finland's longest ski slopes - perfect for those who want to ski in some ski whilst on their Lapland adventure. </li>
<li>Beautiful scenery can be found at this resort due its location within a National Park. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas" class="c-btn">View Yllas resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Saariselka</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108682/saariselkadecember-500x330.jpg" alt="SaariselkaDecember" data-udi="umb://media/1a4308a78fff4a7d80264925a876062b" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Enjoy some true peace and quiet, bar the local wildlife and enjoy an afternoon snowshoeing across the magnificent landscape.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">View Saariselka resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Levi</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108681/levidecember-500x330.jpg" alt="LeviDecember" data-udi="umb://media/6e988ffa5b734036905817b4c7407b66" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Levi enjoys the traditional ski past time of apres-ski and there are plenty of bars (including those which specialise in Karaoke) to enjoy. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">View Levi resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>Best Lapland accommodation in January</h3>
<p>Here we have selected a highlighted accommodation option per the above resorts to give you an overview of the range of accommodation options you will will find available in Lapland.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Central Apartments</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi"><strong>Levi</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108777/levi-central-aprt-338x182.jpg" alt="LeviCentral" data-udi="umb://media/209f4e1c3ee045b79c4f0616758b8cc0" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Great location near the foot of the ski slopes, each apartment comes with its own sauna.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b7f91dba21aa4d17bbb6c42864f4f538" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7f91dba21aa4d17bbb6c42864f4f538}" title="Levi Central Apartments" class="c-btn">View Central Apartments</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Star Arctic Hotel</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka"><strong>Saariselka</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13096222/star_arctic_2023_-15-1.jpg" alt="StarArcticHotel" data-udi="umb://media/cde3ddfe796c4d2787b2dc00c89c6236" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Offering suites and cabins with all the amenities that a hotel provides.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77}" title="Star Arctic Hotel" class="c-btn">View Star Arctic</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Yllasrinne Cabins</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"><strong>Yllas</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13104626/yllasrinne-cabin-villa-yllas-a-exterior.jpg" alt="YllasrinneCabins" data-udi="umb://media/b83e1ca8e26f4b38b857a288e1d2d87d" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Full of charm and character, surrounded by a snowy forest - the perfect escape. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/d121ac73561a4ce18c53f380afb41c87" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d121ac73561a4ce18c53f380afb41c87}" title="Ylläsrinne Cabins" class="c-btn">View Yllasrinne Cabins</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Lapland short breaks</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13055703/finland_lapland_saariselka_reindeer-safari.jpg" alt="LaplandShortBreaks" data-udi="umb://media/37d9f7fa503042e797534e202bbf7259" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af62c53024f64f578d3ed3c88ddb4a9b}" title="Lapland Short Breaks" class="c-btn" data-="">View short break holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
